==== 非洲 ====
*{{flagicon|Senegal}} '''[[塞内加尔|塞内加尔]][[達喀爾|達喀爾]]'''
2018年2月6日，塞内加尔宣布了举办奥运会的兴趣。塞内加尔奥林匹克和体育委员会主席马马杜·恩迪亚耶说：“我们最近翻新或建造了很多体育设施和基础设施。”<ref>{{Cite web|title=Senegal To Bid For First Youth Olympic Games In Africa In 2022|url=https://gamesbids.com/eng/featured/senegal-bid-first-youth-olympic-games-africa-2022/|accessdate=2020-12-30|date=2018-02-08|last=Livingstone|first=Robert|work=GamesBids.com|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109043237/https://gamesbids.com/eng/featured/senegal-bid-first-youth-olympic-games-africa-2022/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

